e fusion product 1/13 was detected. Further, for the recently described East African serotine, L. kirinyaga, we present the second record for West Africa. The cytochrome b sequence of our N. guineensis specimen from Ivory Coast showed 4% divergence to that of its closest relative, N. somalica from Kenya.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Volleth, Marianne", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mayer, Frieder", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Heller, Klaus-Gerhard", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "M\u00fcller, Stefan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fahr, Jakob", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3ed90c3d3dd431d0238441c84eb3b4ca", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/40daa8703304b68e98a1da3bb2f81e34d429c09539f04842d1d146686d38684f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/4YSJRWHX", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/4YSJRWHX", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9dad4b31d2b69455986aec1e105489ae!/b228125-230592", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "title": "Acta Chiropterologica", "volume": "25"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3ed90c3d3dd431d0238441c84eb3b4ca"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:54355